<h1>PHP/HTML5 Contact Form</h1>
This is a simple HTML5 contact form that uses PHP to submit/send the form content by email to a selected recipient (or recipients). It also makes use of the Google reCAPTCHA (http://www.google.com/recaptcha) to prevent spam.

<h2>Important source files</h2>
contact.php - Contains the HTML form
style.css - basic styling for the form
bin/contact.php - Contains the PHP that processes the form
bin/recaptchalib.php - Google reCAPTCHA code

